		<h2>Levels</h2>
		<p>Levels are another way to keep track of how active you (and others) have been. The more points you accumulate, the higher your level.   Searchadoctor Answers recognizes your level achievements with our special brand of thank you's!</p>
		<p>And finally, as you attain higher levels, you'll also be able to contribute more to Searchadoctor Answers - you can ask, answer, vote and rate more frequently.</p>

